    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>This tenebrous apparition, likely one of several called forth when the puppet theater Shadowplay is activated by its operator, stands around 5-feet-fall and resembles a much-larger version of the two-dimensional cutouts used within the purple box or, indeed, any puppet theater. It prefers to flit between shadowy recesses and remain close to walls so that it can go unnoticed or be mistaken for any regular old mundane shadow. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong style=\"color:#191813;font-style:italic\">Rule Clarification, Shadowplay.</strong><span style=\"color:#191813;font-style:italic\"> Full rules for the puppet shadow can be found in  @Compendium[ddd-beginner-baubles.items.bPSgYEe1t53Eo2mt]{Shadowplay}.</span></p>\n</blockquote>",
